---
import MiFoto from "../../assets/img/MiFoto.png";
---

<!-- Contenedor principal -->
<div
  class="mx-auto mt-20 flex max-w-6xl flex-col items-center gap-8 px-6 lg:flex-row "
>
  <!-- Imagen -->
  <div
    class="border-primary h-64 w-64 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl shadow-lg md:h-96 md:w-96 drop-shadow-[4px_4px_0_#7836cf]"
  >
    <img
      src={MiFoto.src}
      alt="Foto de Denesh"
      class="h-full w-full object-cover"
    />
  </div>

  <!-- Texto -->
  <div class="flex-1 text-center text-gray-300 lg:text-left">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">
      My name is <span class="text-white text-shadow">Denesh</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-4">
      I am a robotics software developer specializing in autonomous systems and AI-driven solutions. With over 3 years of experience, my focus lies in applying AI to solve robotics challenges, particularly in physical applications like autonomous driving and manufacturing. I work with technologies including Python, ROS, C++, TensorFlow, and various robotics frameworks.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-2">
      My interest in <span class="text-primary font-semibold"
        >technology</span
      > and
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold">programming</span> began during
      my studies in
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold"
        >Engineering Physics</span
      > at
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold">IIT Madras</span>. My passion for
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold">robotics</span> and
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold">autonomous systems</span> led me to
      pursue a
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold">Master's in Robotics</span> at
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold">TU Delft</span>, specializing in
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold">learning control</span>.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-2">
      I am always committed to <span class="text-primary font-semibold"
        >continuous growth</span
      > and
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold">improvement</span> in my skills,
      seeking to adapt to new
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold">technological advances</span> and excel
      at both
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold">professional</span> and <span
        class="text-primary font-semibold">personal</span
      > levels.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
